    <div class="post" itemprop="articleBody">
     <p>
      2h enhance is very awkward mainly due to windfury. In game terms it is very easy to just
      <br/>
      make maelstrom weapon trigger twice for 2h weapons, and just remove flame thong, which no one cares about. However, the concept of windfury is that you are using the element of wind to make your weapon spin and delivery a flurry of blows.
     </p>
     <p>
      While this concept is easy to pull off with an 1h weapon, since you can just spin the weapon on one hand, it gets super awkward on 2 handed weapons, which basically can‚Äôt rotate on that axis at all without the handle going all over the place and you basically needing to get away from your own weapon.
     </p>
    </div>
