    <div class="post" itemprop="articleBody">
     <p>
      I would love it because I still have the occasional dream where I am back in AV with my TuF, deleting people to the shadowlands.
     </p>
     <p>
      But if I am practical, it would be too much work and feel horribly lumpy unless you stacked a boatload of haste, and I think scaling would make you preying so hard on procs to be competitive most would find it boring outside of meme random BG YouTube highlight reels.
     </p>
     <p>
      I mean you can play 2H enh right now if you want - it‚Äôs called ret paladin in Wotlk classic. Same big burst, same proc reliance, same waiting on windfu‚Ä¶seal of command to go brrrr.
     </p>
