    <div class="post" itemprop="articleBody">
     <p>
      The way Windfury and Stormstrike currently work, it wouldn‚Äôt matter if you had a 2h or not.  Windfury no longer is scaled with weapon damage, but with attack power.
     </p>
     <p>
      However, transmog for 2h would solve a lot of people‚Äôs desires to see their shaman wielding a 2h again, and it‚Äôs been discussed on the shaman forum and brought up in the wow council according to posts there.
     </p>
